@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = course-alex-local-token

### The required local profile stays keyless and labels generation as disabled.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/health

### Reset, seed, and index the Support Knowledge Assistant.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/reset

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/seed

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/index

### GENERATION route: grounded answer generation uses ai.providers.generation.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/query
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What should I do if failed sign-ins locked me out?"
}

### ORCHESTRATION route: intent and action planning use ai.providers.orchestration.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Why is ticket T-1001 unresolved?",
  "conversationId": "course-provider-routing"
}

### With the openai profile, confirm both purpose routes and models without exposing a key.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/health

